{{!
    @template   report_adeptus_insights/support_ticket_detail

    Support ticket detail view template showing ticket information,
    conversation thread, and reply functionality.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "wwwroot": "https://example.com",
        "ticket": {"id": 1, "subject": "Test", "status": "open"}
    }

